body:
### Who Are We?

SparkysRunawayCircuitCrew is a group of high school students, in a team designing a robot for the 2015 Sparkfun AVC competition. All of our code is right there for you to take a look at, so go ahead!! And if you happen to think of anything, feel free to shoot me an email at <benscholer3248511@gmail.com>!! Have a great day!!
